<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,151,536]" pageId="5" pageNumber="454">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,439,464]" pageId="5" pageNumber="454">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species resembles 
<taxonomicName authority="(Wiedemann)" authorityName="Wiedemann" baseAuthorityName="Wiedemann" baseAuthorityYear="1830" box="[602,1013,439,464]" class="Insecta" family="Muscidae" genus="Pygophora" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="macularis">
